Package: CAPaidFamilyLeave
Title: California Paid Family Leave and Female Labor Force Participation
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Dia", "Talwar", email = "diatalwar21@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Replication package for the ECON 620 capstone. Estimates the
    effect of California's 2004 Paid Family Leave law on female labor force
    participation using Synthetic Difference-in-Differences
    (Arkhangelsky et al. 2021).
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Imports:
    synthdid,
    dplyr
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    here
